<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    <hr>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
      <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile-image", class: "profile-image" %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div 
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<% skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%;"
                >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>Nam non leo id est consequat aliquam. Morbi semper nulla erat, sit amet interdum leo aliquet quis. Donec convallis, elit non blandit faucibus, nunc nisl commodo ipsum, sed hendrerit tellus orci sed justo.</p>
        <p>Morbi dapibus nisl neque, semper blandit lectus fringilla in. Vivamus ex tortor, posuere sit amet placerat et, vulputate quis orci. Fusce euismod enim sed metus scelerisque varius. Donec lobortis enim rutrum tristique dictum. Quisque blandit laoreet ante vitae molestie.</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 2
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 3
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 2
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>